      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Constant-Velocity : Specify Two Positions</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Constant-Velocity | Two Position</text></para>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="AStandard" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="cell-padding:0px; border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; cell-border-width:0px; border-style:none;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">This is the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Flexible-Polynomial</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> motion-law. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">Use the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Control-Buttons</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Blend-PointEditor-ControlButtons" styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">Blend-Point Editor</link><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> or the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-SegmentEditor-Segment-Parameters" styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">Segment Editor</link><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> to define its </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Start-Position</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> and its </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">End-Position</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">. All other motion-values are NOT specified.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">This motion-law is </text><text styleclass="Interface2" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">not</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> defined with a </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">You need to manually specify the motion-value of the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">End-Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> at the end of the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Previous-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> to equal the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Start-Velocity</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> of this Constant-Velocity segment, to avoid a Velocity discontinuity.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Flexible-Polynomial : Two Position | Constant-Velocity</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="3" colcount="1" style="cell-padding:1px;">
